From Friday night to sunset on Saturday, the markets, shops and public transport cease their activity.
And the work week starts on Sunday morning.
Many cafes, restaurants and hotels serve only cashew food, which excludes pork, seafood, fish without scales and dishes made up of both milk and meat.
