How can you protect yourself?
Preservatives may reduce the risk of infection, but do not protect 100%.
The reason is that pathogens of sexually transmitted diseases can also be transmitted through lubricant infection or close body contact.
The experts therefore recommend that anyone who often changes sex partners regularly pass examinations.
