In young people, I love the work that Leo Arill does.
For you, what is your greatest success in the federation?
Having been one of the most glorious times of the national team between 1988 and 1995, and the fact that in the early 1990s the NSB had up to 17 teams in one season.
What do you have to do?
There are things I would have wanted to put in place, such as the regionalization of the minor categories.
